      <div class="info-row"><span class="key">Repo</span><span class="val">max-diver999/invest-gulf-website</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="key">GA4</span><span class="val">G-H725E249H7 · 540367626</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="key">GSC</span><span class="val">sc-domain:mexico-invest.com</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="key">Lead API</span><span class="val">POST /api/lead/ → 200</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card">
      <h3>Indexing status (5 Jun)</h3>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="key">GSC sitemap</span><span class="val">✓ 0 errors</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="key">Bing sitemap</span><span class="val">✓ Success</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="key">Google API</span><span class="val">200 / 201 URL</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="key">IndexNow</span><span class="val">201 / 201 URL</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="key">indexing-bot SA</span><span class="val">Owner in GSC</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="key">MCP</span><span class="val">GSC + GA4 + Bing</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-title">Launch timeline</div>
  <div>
    <div class="changelog-item">
      <div class="changelog-date">5 Jun 2026</div>
      <div>
        <div class="changelog-title">🚀 Launch Day — 201 URLs live + full indexing push</div>
        <div class="changelog-desc">Batch 2–5 RE guides + 9 comparisons deployed (commit a30b5e4). Google Indexing API 200 URL + Bing IndexNow 201 URL. GSC + Bing sitemap verified. Site-report v1.0 published. fideicomiso HUB 3 322 words. INDEXING_SETUP_CHECKLIST added to templates.</div>
        <div class="changelog-tags"><span class="tag green">Launch</span><span class="tag blue">Indexing</span><span class="tag amber">Report v1.0</span></div>
